<span style="font-size: 1.6em; margin-left: 0.2em;">'''Know before you start'''</span><br><br>
* '''Prerequisites:''' You should be familiar with the programming language that user scripts are written in i.e., '''JavaScript.''' It's also preferable to have some understanding of '''jQuery.'''
*  As part of the tour, you will send some messages to your own MediaWiki user pages automatically.<br>
* This tour '''only''' uses the Source Editor. If you use the Visual Editor or have it enabled it won't work yet.<br>
* You need JavaScript enabled for the tour to work properly. If you're using Internet Explorer, you need to be updated to IE 10.<br>
* The tour is not supported on tablets and smaller mobile devices.
</div>
